          <img
            src="/portfolio.webp"
            alt="A website with three images at full height with a category name displayed on each image."
            class="rounded-lg"
          />
        </a>
        <h3 class="sub-heading">Photo Portfolio</h3>
        <span class="pill">Design & Code</span>
        <p class="pb-4">
          I worked with a client to create a design tailored to their needs. The
          result is a portfolio website built with Astro and Tailwind CSS. I
          combined everything I had learned so far and put it to practice, and
          used this project to learn more about accessible web design.
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://elviraholmberg.netlify.app"
          target="_blank"
          class="btn btn-hover self-center mt-auto focus-indicator">Live demo</a
        >
      </div>

