            class="rounded-lg"
          />
        </a>
        <h3 class="sub-heading">Running Planner</h3>
        <span class="pill">Design & Code</span>
        <p class="pb-4">
          I built a running app that allows the user to plan and view future
          workouts as well as access relevant weather information via an API. My
          aim was to create a personalised user experience. The app was built
          using Vue.js and Tailwind CSS.
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://prerun.netlify.app/#/"
          target="_blank"
          class="btn btn-hover self-center mt-auto focus-indicator">Live demo</a
        >
